"2.2.Multi-Token Prediction Inspired by Gloeckle et al. (2024), we investigate and set a Multi-Token Prediction (MTP) objective for DeepSeek-V3, which extends the prediction scope to multiple future tokens at each position.On the one hand, an MTP objective densifies the training signals and may improve data efficiency.On the other hand, MTP may enable the model to pre-plan its representations for better prediction of future tokens.Figure 3 illustrates our implementation of MTP.Different from Gloeckle et al. (2024), which parallelly predicts 𝐷additional tokens using independent output heads, we sequentially predict additional tokens and keep the complete causal chain at each prediction depth.We introduce the details of our MTP implementation in this section.MTP Modules.",110,778,194,10,10,"[-1.17853850e-01 -4.66265716e-02  9.63973626e-02  3.51839289e-02
